---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import ContactButton from "../components/utils/ContactButton.html";
import MoHeadshot from "../assets/mo-headshot.avif";
import NancyHeadshot from "../assets/nancy-headshot.avif";
import SloaneHeadshot from "../assets/sloane-headshot.jpg";
import LinkedInLogo from "../assets/LI-Logo.png";
import ShrmPS from "../assets/shrm-ps.png";
---

<Layout>
  <Header />
  <div class="w-full mx-auto">
    <div
      class="pt-38 px-10 pb-18 bg-linear-to-br from-warm-green to-cool-green"
    >
      <p class="text-center text-white text-3xl lg:text-5xl manrope-bold">
        The Team
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="container mx-auto md:px-30 bg-white md:w-3/4 pt-8 manrope-light"
    >
      <p class="mb-6">
        IFO, a leading provider of facilitators and related group facilitation
        services, exists to provide training, certification, marketing services,
        education, and community for peer group facilitators at all stages of
        their career.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Our mission is to support 1 billion people in peer groups by 2053
        because we believe peer groups have the transformative power to provide
        every person with a place to learn and grow in a supportive community.
        Peer groups teach important skills for empathy, vulnerability, that
        enable meaningful connections and growth. The transformative power of
        forum has the exponential potential to change how we see ourselves, each
        other, the world, and our place within it. We support communities so
        communities can support the world.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6">
        In the video below, IFO Founder & President Mo Fathelbab explains his
        vision and purpose for IFO. Have questions for our team? Learn more
        about the benefits of beginning your journey with IFO by reaching out
        today!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto md:px-20 bg-white py-5 md:w-3/4">
      <!-- width="827"
        height="465" -->
      <iframe
        class="w-full h-100"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/5W_gt2_gyqU"
        title="Introducing IFO"
        frameborder="2"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
        referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>

    <ContactButton />

    <div class="container mx-auto lg:px-30 bg-white md:flex md:flex-row gap-2">
      <div class="md:w-1/2 text-center justify-center">
        <img
          src={MoHeadshot.src}
          alt="photo of Mo Fathelbab"
          class="w-2/3 mx-auto md:w-full"
        />
        <p class="py-6 text-2xl solway-medium">Mo Fathelbab</p>
        <p
          class="mb-6 manrope-light text-pretty md:w-5/6 mx-auto lg:px-4 leading-8"
        >
          Mo is an expert facilitator and trusted advisor with decades of
          experience helping leaders build authentic connections and
          high-performing peer groups. He specializes in creating safe,
          transformative spaces where participants can learn, share, and grow
          together.
        </p>

        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mofathelbab/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <img src={LinkedInLogo.src} width="110" class="mx-auto pb-10" />
        </a>

        <div class="pb-4 w-fit mx-auto">
          <p class="pb-4">Mo's weekly podcast:</p>
          <a
            href="https://www.shrm.org/topics-tools/flagships/people-strategy"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            <img src={ShrmPS.src} width="130" class="mx-auto pb-10" />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="md:w-1/2 text-center border-t-1 md:border-t-0 border-gray-300 pt-10 md:pt-0"
      >
        <img
          src={NancyHeadshot.src}
          alt="photo of Nancy Koleda"
          class="w-2/3 mx-auto md:w-full"
        />

        <p class="py-6 text-2xl solway-medium">Nancy Koleda</p>
        <p
          class="mb-6 manrope-light text-pretty md:w-5/6 mx-auto lg:px-4 leading-8"
        >
          Nancy is a seasoned facilitator and leadership coach with deep
          experience guiding executives and teams through transformational
          growth. She brings a thoughtful, practical approach to training,
          helping leaders strengthen communication, build trust, and foster
          meaningful collaboration.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nancy-koleda-2349585/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <img src={LinkedInLogo.src} width="110" class="mx-auto pb-10" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div
        class="md:w-1/2 text-center border-t-1 md:border-t-0 border-gray-300 pt-10 md:pt-0"
      >
        <img
          src={SloaneHeadshot.src}
          alt="photo of Sloane Kaplan"
          class="w-2/3 mx-auto md:w-full"
        />

        <p class="py-6 text-2xl solway-medium">Sloane Kaplan</p>
        <p
          class="mb-6 manrope-light text-pretty md:w-5/6 mx-auto lg:px-4 leading-8"
        >
          Sloane is passionate about people, details, and getting things
          doneâ€”with heart and humor. Owing to her background in hospitality,
          office administration, and international volunteer work, she
          approaches every challenge with clarity, care, and a deep commitment
          to making things, and people, better than she found them.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sloane-kaplan-52a14817/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <img src={LinkedInLogo.src} width="110" class="mx-auto pb-10" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
